// SuperDuck Go workspace.
//
// Defines all Go modules in this monorepo so contributors can develop the
// CLI / native-host / MCP server (and future Go subprojects like coworkd)
// together with a single `go build ./...` from the repo root, and so
// editors / agents pick up the right module roots automatically.
//
// Toolchain pin matches chrome-native-host/go.mod and the version installed
// in .devcontainer. Bump both in lockstep when upgrading Go.

go 1.25

use ./chrome-native-host
